  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="AN128.1-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">iravukkuṟit (RK: iravukkuṟi vanta; C2+3: ______ta) talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat 
            (RK: talaimakaḷ) tōḻikkuc colluvāḷāyt talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">What SHE said as one speaking to the confidante 
            when HE was behind the fence during the night tryst.</p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="AN128.1">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>maṉṟupā ṭavintu maṉaimaṭin taṉṟē</l>
                <l>koṉṟō raṉṉa koṭumaiyō ṭiṉṟē</l>
                <l>yāmaṅ koḷavariṟ kaṉai<supplied>i</supplied>k kāmaṅ</l>
                <l>kaṭaliṉu muraiik karaipoḻi yummē</l>
                <l>yevaṉkol vāḻi tōḻi mayaṅki</l>
                <l>yiṉṉa mākavu naṉṉar neñca</l>
                <l>meṉṉoṭu niṉṉoṭuñ cūḻātu kaimik</l>
                <l>kiṟumpupaṭ ṭiruḷiya viṭṭaruñ cilampiṟ</l>
                <l>kuṟuñcuṉaik kuvaḷai vaṇṭupaṭac cūṭik</l>
                <l>kāṉa nāṭaṉ varūum yāṉaik</l>
                <l>kayiṟṟuppuṟat taṉṉa kaṉmicaic ciṟuneṟi</l>
                <l>māri vāṉan talaii nīrvār</l>
                <l>piṭṭaruṅ kaṇṇa paṭukuḻi yiyavi</l>
                <l>ṉiruḷiṭai mitippuḻi nōkkiyavar</l>
                <l>taḷaraṭi tāṅkiya ceṉṟa tiṉṟē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l>As the singing/commotion on the village common ended, the house subsided. (1)</l>
                <l>If today, with the cruelty of those who have killed,</l>
                <l>midnight comes to overtake [me, my] passion, intense,</l>
                <l>will talk [louder] than the sea [and] overflow the shore. (2-4)</l>
                <l>What, oh friend? (5)</l>
                <l>Although we are like that, confused, [my] good heart, (6)</l>
                <l>peering [ahead] while treading in the midst of darkness</l>
                <l>for the way with pits found in narrow places that are difficult [to pass],</l>
                <l>as showers were bestowed on the forest, water overflowing,</l>
                <l>has gone today in order to support his slackening feet (12-15)</l>
                <l>on the small paths high in the boulders, like the roped backs of elephants,</l> 
                <l>where the man from a land of forests comes,</l>
                <l>wearing, for bees to frequent, water lilies from the small pools</l>
                <l>of the mountain flank difficult [to approach], completely  darkened since very overgrown</l> 
                <l>with thickets, not considering me or you. (7-11)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
